REMEMBER:
log format:
if self error: self function name - source of error - error
if chained error : self function name - error

authorization -
    header(checked) : Bearer <token>
refresh -
    cookie(checked) : <token>
csrf -
    header(checked) : csrf <token>
    cookie(checked) : <token>
mfa -
    header(checked) : mfa <token>
    cookie(skipped) : <token>

200: (ok, soft reject or accept)
401: (reject, user not authenticated)
403: (reject, user needs mfa completed)
422: (reject, incomplete body, frontend code error)
429: (reject, rate limited)
500: (server internal error)
502/504: (server unavailable)

